Do you have any kind of database of your clips, Steve?  I have many good examples but no 
organization (other than keeping the clips from a session, or a day, grouped together in 
the same folder).  It&#39;s hard for me to keep track of everything.  Eons ago, I used to create 
simple databases with Filemaker Pro.  I&#39;ve been thinking lately, I need to come up with 
something to use as references for the details for various clips.  I&#39;d be interested in 
knowing what, if anything, others are using.  

Margaret 

